Tanzania Stock Exchange Suspends Nicol From Trading Its Shares for a Month

-- B y   D a v i d   M a l i n g h a   D o y a
-- 
2011-06-07T04:29:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-07/tanzania-stock-exchange-suspends-nicol-from-trading-its-shares-for-a-month.html
The Dar es Salaam Stock Exchange
suspended National Investment Co. from trading for one month
after the Tanzanian company failed to submit its financial
results for 2009 and 2010.  The suspension takes effect today, the Dar es Salaam-based
bourse said in a statement published in the Daily News newspaper
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Malingha Doya in Dar es Salaam at 
 dmalingha@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  